clusters do not contribute to the number of isolated massive sink\nparticles, as the gravitational softening in the calculation suppresses this\nprocess.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Jun 2011 20:02:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
