re-processing then the lag corresponding to a light travel time\nacross 30 R_g. Some of the remaining observations have similar energy spectra\nand covariance spectra, but none of them show a significant QPO, so we conclude\nthat none of these features are the trigger for the appearance of the QPO in\nthis object.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Jun 2011 09:34:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
